{"tid":2403162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(聯署要人)反對正苦要求筲箕灣官立中學師生進行強制檢測聯署聲明","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T10:12:16.000Z","uid":78222,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b6358f7a6d28e1ae2e8537bbf356a956e0b46630","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><ins>1.聯署link</ins></span></span><br />\n反對正苦要求筲箕灣官立中學師生進行強制檢測聯署聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://linktr.ee/Sfuhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2FSfuhk&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=75f66653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://linktr.ee/Sfuhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><ins>2. IG post share </ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLHsHaIBzXB/?igshid=1smm1c666qhom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLHsHaIBzXB%2F%3Figshid%3D1smm1c666qhom&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=92605f8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLHsHaIBzXB%2F%3Figshid%3D1smm1c666qhom&h=f6926bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLHsHaIBzXB/?igshid=1smm1c666qhom</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><ins>3.事源</ins></span></span><br />\n住惠利兩人確診 曾回校考試　<br />\n筲官135師生隔離營過年<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/JRDFHKD5HVEC5M4GVTCC2OHUJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FJRDFHKD5HVEC5M4GVTCC2OHUJ4%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=dabb6b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FJRDFHKD5HVEC5M4GVTCC2OHUJ4%2F&h=aede2275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/JRDFHKD5HVEC5M4GVTCC2OHUJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣官立中學兩名居於疫廈鰂魚涌惠利大廈的中六學生先後染疫，由於二人傳染期曾回校考試，衞生防護中心擔心校內或有環境傳播，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">決定將130名同場考試的中六學生及五名教職員隔離檢疫，農曆新年須在隔離營度過。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">今次係筲箕灣官立中學開先列<br />\n大家再唔出聲 之後就會再有更多學校<br />\n跟住就到你屋企</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">4.過往新聞</span></span></ins><br />\n筲箕灣官立中學全校學生唱完校歌大叫「光復香港，時代革命！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536060</a>"},{"pid":"37c5b6d2d265ecf5038afd5832505e86e1df0e9f","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"聯署未必有用<br />\n但咩都唔做就只會令敵人不斷打壓"},{"pid":"811551e2faea6641b965ae57576c595992ddb35c","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"我見未有post<br />\n路過嘅手足可以幫手推上去嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd27408ac9b1ea4d8b5f47174710762b40daa235","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512e79e0e8723740ec6d761119aa9712bacf802b","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"路過幫手簽同推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要多啲人關注"},{"pid":"602b85630701a4844e509c4bdd939f0998951b9f","tid":2403162,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 求幫手推兩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore